---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ScheduleACallButton from "../ScheduleACallButton.astro";
---

<section id="pwa-expertise" class="wrapper section">
  <header>
    <p class="section-tag">
      <Image
        src="/images/icons/rocket.svg"
        alt="Bar Chart Icon"
        width="30"
        height="30"
      />
      Built to Scale, Designed to Last
    </p>
  </header>
  <div class="columns">
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Comprehensive Code Audit</h2>
      <p>
        Before we start optimizing, we conduct a thorough audit of your existing
        codebase. This includes analyzing the current structure, identifying
        areas of technical debt, and pinpointing potential scalability issues.
        Our audit helps us understand your specific needs and lays the
        foundation for a robust and scalable solution.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Implementation of Best Practices</h2>
      <p>
        We adhere to industry best practices in coding standards, including
        modularization, clear naming conventions, and DRY (Don't Repeat
        Yourself) principles. These practices not only make your code easier to
        understand and maintain but also reduce the likelihood of bugs and
        errors. Our goal is to create a clean, organized codebase that supports
        long-term growth and scalability.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Modular Architecture Design</h2>
      <p>
        A modular architecture is critical to a scalable and maintainable
        codebase. We design your application with modular components that can be
        easily updated, replaced, or scaled independently. This approach allows
        your app to grow and adapt to changing requirements without major
        overhauls.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Performance Optimization</h2>
      <p>
        We focus on optimizing your code for performance, ensuring that your
        application remains fast and responsive as it scales. This includes
        techniques such as code splitting, lazy loading, and efficient resource
        management. By optimizing performance from the start, we ensure that
        your application delivers a smooth user experience, even under heavy
        load.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Comprehensive Documentation</h2>
      <p>
        Clear, comprehensive documentation is essential for maintaining a
        scalable codebase. We document every aspect of your codebase, including
        architecture decisions, coding standards, and key components. This
        documentation serves as a valuable resource for your development team,
        making it easier to onboard new developers and maintain the application
        over time.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="block">
      <h2>Ongoing Support and Training</h2>
      <p>
        Our commitment doesn't end with the initial setup. We provide ongoing
        support to help you manage and maintain your codebase as your
        application evolves. We also offer training sessions for your
        development team, ensuring they are equipped with the knowledge and
        skills needed to keep your codebase in top condition. This ongoing
        partnership ensures that your application remains scalable and
        maintainable long into the future.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>
      <strong>
        A strong, scalable codebase is the backbone of any successful web
        application.
      </strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      Let us help you build a foundation that will support your business growth
      for years to come.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <ScheduleACallButton />
  </div>
</section>
